<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.5.2">
<l>kaṭañcūḻ kariyum parimāvu molimān</l>
<l>tēruṅ kālāḷum</l>
<l>uṭaṉcūḻn teḻunta kaṭiyilaṅkai</l>
<l>poṭiyā vaṭivāyc caranturantāṉ</l>
<l>iṭamcūḻn teṅku miruvicumpi</l>
<l>limaiyōr vaṇaṅka maṇaṅkamaḻum</l>
<l>taṭamcūḻn teṅku maḻakāya</l>
<l>cāḷak kirāma maṭaineñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Heart, take refuge at Śālagrāma which is beautiful everywhere,</l>
<l rend="indent">surrounded by pools where scents waft,</l>
<l>As unblinking [celestials] worship in the vast skies everywhere,</l>
<l rend="indent">surrounded by heaven,</l>
<l>[The place of] him who shot a sharp-tipped arrow,</l>
<l rend="indent">the way fortified Lanka perished,</l>
<l>[And] where arose assembled together ichor-enveloped elephants, horses,</l>
<l rend="indent">thundering horse[-drawn] chariots, and foot soldiers.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
